text: Antonov An-24 is soviet built twin-engine transport aircraft. It is used by both airlines and air forces. It is a short takeoff and landing aircraft. It is built under licence in China like Y-7. An-26 is a modernized variant. == Bibliography == * == Similar aircraft == * Airtech CN-235 * Casa C-295 Category:Soviet & Russian aircraft Category:Soviet military aircraft
